{"tid":1802866,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"校長們，同學們，係時候企出來公民抗命，對楊潤雄說不！","createTime":"2019-12-29T18:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T23:44:01.000Z","uid":344847,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32de164f19f6893042b0d3c136dc9226aacd14d5","tid":1802866,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T18:39:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">定係校長會選擇淆底？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「被問到若要求學校對教師進行調查，學校卻不配合，甚至校長也支持教師行為，局方如何應對；楊潤雄表示，若教育局認為校長已不能勝任，可以取消其校長資格。」<br />\n<br />\n噉樣如果所有校長都企出來反對「配合」未審先判呢，係咪抄L哂佢哋呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">經驗告訴我們，中大校長段崇智成為全港唯一大學校長肯為學生挺身而出向黑警說不，最後還得到《泰晤士高等教育》青睞而名列年度全球高等教育風雲人物，唔係因為佢真係有噉嘅智慧和勇氣呀！佢係被吳傲雪和其他中大學生擺上枱逼上梁山，終於無奈才敢企出來㗎！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">孤掌難鳴，校長係唔會敢自己企出來同強權隻揪㗎！係噉，大家識做喇？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec903577f9b82de5c34342ed1e45e2a95e841336","tid":1802866,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T18:40:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b7680c5b3173507d4f50195f07981a51c78884d1","tid":1802866,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c44bc5f4542b871900854ebfe6ec11a52aae4f5","tid":1802866,"uid":136550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T20:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a37db2357c1b58ce05f4cbd189caf32100562a9","tid":1802866,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"